Scirate Reloaded: re-write of Dave Bacon's original www.scirate.com
crowd-sourcing the daily routine of selecting the interesting arXiv-papers

using the Django/Python web-framework
started in January 2012 by Christian Schaffner (huebli@gmail.com)
(let me know if you wanna help!)


Install instructions:
* install https://bitbucket.org/ubernostrum/django-registration/

* rename settings.py.template to settings.py
* adjust database and template paths in settings.py
* adjust mail settings in settings.py

* run "python manage.py syncdb" to create the database and load the fixtures

